divs: sighting detailsi was standing in my back yard looking nw when i noticed a bright orange-crystaline object. object was stationary. it was visable to me for about 5 seconds, and then just "blinked out". this object was similar to the objects we saw 4\16\05 in same area of sky, at approximitly the same time. color and intensity of the objects were the same. this object was seen at 21:20. my reaction to this event was one of awe and wonderment! after the april sighting, i really didn't think i would see another one.
Summary: Saw bright orange light in NW sky. Object stationary. Visual for about 5 sec. Similar to 4/16/05 sighting. Same area.
